  "description": "<i>Dread Dragon Droom</i> is an educational game which tells the story about the Princess Arminda who has been kidnapped by the dragon Droom and her love Prince Henry who has been turned into a frog. The objective is to save the princess and restore the prince to his human form.<br><br>The story is told through text screens with some graphics and to advance the story puzzles have to be solved. There are a few different characters that the player will meet including a wizard, a witch and some fairies and the player drives a car between the houses of these characters. The game is divided into thirteen chapters that each can be started on its own. Most of the puzzles are mathematical or logical while some involve remembering spells and passwords.",
